In the Matter of COATES, BENNETT & REIDENBACH, Inc., Bankrupts. Genessee Valley Trust Company, Appellant. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. May 14, 1926.) No. 370. Peck & Whitbeek and E. C. Whitbeck, all of Rochester, N. Y., for appellant. Hubbell, Taylor, Goodwin & Moser and C. L. Clinton, all of Rochester, N. Y., for appellee.

Before ROGERS, MANTON, and HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order (8 F.[2d] 757) reversed in open court.
